WITH v_prod AS (          
         SELECT
            LISTAGG(
                CASE
                    WHEN vpj.product_name IS NOT NULL THEN vpj.product_name ||
                    case when vlf.formulation is not null or (vpj.concentration_text is not null and vluj.unit is not null ) then '(' ||
                        case when vlf.formulation is not null then vlf.formulation end ||
                        case when (vpj.concentration_text is not null and vluj.unit is not null ) then ', ' end ||
                        vpj.concentration_text ||
                        vluj.unit ||
                        ')'
                    END
                END,
            CHR(10) ) WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY vpj.product_name) AS DELIVERY_QUANTITY
        FROM
            (SELECT
                gtt.code
            FROM
                gtt_filter_key_values gtt
            WHERE
                gtt.key_id = (select KEY_ID from pvr_filter_dict where group_desc='PRODUCT')) gvp
            JOIN vw_product vpj ON (
                gvp.code = vpj.product_id
                and vpj.lang_id=25
            )
            LEFT JOIN vw_prod_form_link vpfl    ON ( 
                       vpfl.product_id = vpj.product_id 
                    AND  
                        vpfl.tenant_id = vpj.tenant_id)

            LEFT JOIN vw_lfor_formulation vlf ON (
                vpfl.formulation_id = vlf.formulation_id
                and vlf.lang_id=25
            )
            left JOIN vw_prod_concentration vpcc ON ( vpcc.product_id = vpj.product_id
                                            AND 
                                                         vpcc.tenant_id = vpj.tenant_id
                                             )
            LEFT JOIN ( SELECT * FROM vw_ldu_unit  WHERE LANG_ID=25) vluj ON (
               vpcc.conc_unit_id = vluj.unit_id
            and 
                vpcc.tenant_id = vluj.tenant_id
            )
            ) , v_reg_pmda_auth AS (
                SELECT  distinct
                    case_id,
                    tenant_id,
                    version_num
                FROM
                     reg_pmda_auth_identification
                WHERE REPORT_TYPE_ID in (1,2)
                UNION
                SELECT 1, 1, 1 FROM dual
            ),
        conservative_listedness AS (
                select mdr_ae_pt_code, pkg_pvr_app_util.f_conservative_listedness(null,NULL,mdr_ae_pt_code) conser_listedness 
            from (select distinct mdr_ae_pt_code from v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai
            where exists (select 1 from gtt_query_case_list gqcl where gqcl.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND gqcl.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND gqcl.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num)
              and mdr_ae_pt_code is not null
                    )), 
        set_1 AS (
            SELECT
                cai.case_id,
                cai.mdr_ae_soc,
                cai.mdr_ae_soc_code,
                cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                cai.mdr_ae_pt_code,
                cai.mdr_ae_pt,
                cai.ae_rec_num,
                cai.infection,
                DECODE(TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                ' - ',
                 TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_START_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_END_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS REPT_PERIOD,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY
                    cai.case_id,
                    cai.ae_rec_num
                    ORDER BY
                        cai.ae_rec_num desc, psrh.generation_date
                ) rn_1,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY
                    cai.case_id,
                    cai.ae_rec_num
                    ORDER BY
                        psrh.generation_date
                ) rn,
                    CASE
                        WHEN gqcl.case_id IS NULL THEN
                            DENSE_RANK() over (PARTITION BY
                                TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                                ' - ' ||
                                TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD')
                                ORDER BY
                                    psrh.generation_date)
                        ELSE 0
                    END
                AS rn2,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY
                    cai.case_id,
                    cai.mdr_ae_pt
                    ORDER BY
                        cai.ae_Rec_num desc, psrh.generation_date
                ) rn_3
            FROM 
( select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id,
						MAX(processed_report_id) over (partition by case_id,tenant_id,ae_rec_num) processed_report_id,
						version_num version_num,
						agg_report_id agg_report_id
				from gtt_query_case_list ) GQCL
                JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa on (
                NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
                )
               INNER JOIN (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id, 
						MAX(processed_report_id) processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num
				from v_j_ae_iden_reaction
                group by case_id,tenant_id,processed_report_id,ae_rec_num) cai_max
                ON
                (
                  cai_max.case_id = gqcl.case_id
                  AND
                  cai_max.tenant_id = gqcl.tenant_id
                  AND 
                  cai_max.processed_report_id = gqcl.processed_report_id
                  AND
                  cai_max.ae_rec_num = gqcl.ae_rec_num
                )
                INNER JOIN v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai ON (
                        cai_max.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND
                        cai_max.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND
                        cai_max.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND
                        cai_max.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num
                    AND 
                        cai_max.processed_report_id = cai.processed_report_id
                )
                LEFT JOIN conservative_listedness gtt ON ( cai.mdr_ae_pt_code=gtt.mdr_ae_pt_code
      /*                  gqcl.case_id = gtt.case_id

                )

                    gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
                )
        )
       , set_period AS (
            SELECT

                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD'),

                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS REPT_PERIOD,
                psrh.generation_date
            FROM 
            (select distinct gqcl.agg_report_id  from 
            GTT_QUERY_CASE_LIST GQCL
                JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa on (
                NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
                )) gtt
                LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
                    gtt.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
                )
        ) 
        ,set_2 AS (
            SELECT
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                case_id,
                rept_period
            FROM
                set_1
            WHERE
                (rn_1 = 1 and rn_3 = 1 OR rn2 = 1)
        ),set_3 AS (
            SELECT
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                nvl(set_2.rept_period,set_period.rept_period) rept_period,
                DECODE(COUNT(DISTINCT case_id),0,NULL,COUNT(DISTINCT case_id)) AS case_count
            FROM
                set_2
            right join set_period on (set_2.rept_period=set_period.rept_period)
            GROUP BY
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                nvl(set_2.rept_period,set_period.rept_period)
                --rept_period
        ),evt_2 AS (
            SELECT
                case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                DECODE(infection,1,1,0) AS flag_infection,
                rept_period
            FROM

                rn_1 = 1 and rn_3 = 1
        ),evt_3 AS (
          SELECT case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                rept_period,
                COUNT(DISTINCT CASE_ID||'-'||MDR_AE_SOC||'-'||MDR_AE_PT_CODE) EVT_COUNT,

            FROM (   SELECT

                            mdr_ae_pt_code,
                            mdr_ae_pt,
                            rept_period,
                            CASE WHEN ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY CASE_ID,MDR_AE_SOC,MDR_AE_PT_CODE,flag_infection ORDER BY NULL) =1 THEN flag_infection ELSE 0 END flag_infection
                        FROM evt_2 )
            GROUP BY case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                rept_period            
        ) 
        , PSR_FORM_3 AS (SELECT
                set_3.mdr_ae_soc,
                evt_3.mdr_ae_pt,
                DECODE(SET_3.REPT_PERIOD,' - ',
                TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_START_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_END_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                SET_3.REPT_PERIOD
                ) AS REPT_PERIOD,
                set_3.case_count soc_count,
                evt_3.evt_count ||
                CASE
                        WHEN inf_count <> 0   THEN '(' ||
                        inf_count ||
                        ')'
                    END
                AS pt_count,
(	SELECT DISTINCT

WITH v_reg_pmda_auth AS (
SELECT
case_id,
tenant_id,
version_num,
LISTAGG(identification_number,',') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY identification_number) as pmda_number
FROM
(Select distinct case_id,tenant_id,version_num,case when PMDA_NUMBER is not null then REPORT_CATEGORY_DESC||'-'||PMDA_NUMBER end identification_number from V_SUB_MHLW_CSRCASENUM where REGEXP_LIKE(REPORT_CATEGORY_DESC, '^[[:alpha:]]+$')) rpai
GROUP BY
case_id,tenant_id,version_num
union
select 1,1,1,null from dual
), conservative_listedness AS (
				select mdr_ae_pt_code, pkg_pvr_app_util.f_conservative_listedness(null,NULL,mdr_ae_pt_code) conser_listedness 
            from (select distinct mdr_ae_pt_code from v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai
            where exists (select 1 from gtt_query_case_list gqcl where gqcl.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND gqcl.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND gqcl.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num)
          and mdr_ae_pt_code is not null
                    )),
period_det as
(
select gqcl.agg_Report_id,gqcl.tenant_id, dense_rank() over (order by psrh.agg_report_id,psrh.generation_date) as period_num 
from
(select distinct agg_Report_id,tenant_id from gtt_query_case_list) gqcl
LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
				and gqcl.tenant_id = psrh.tenant_id
				))
,set_1 AS (
			SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') || ' - ' || TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS rept_period
			,pd.period_num as period_num
			,case when pfh.rec_num is null then row_number() OVER ( partition by psrh.agg_report_id,psrh.generation_date
				ORDER BY cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id,cai.mdr_ae_pt_code,psrh.submission_date,cai.case_id
				) else pfh.rec_num end as rn,
			dense_rank() over (partition by gqcl.case_id,cai.mdr_ae_soc,cai.mdr_Ae_pt,cai.ae_rec_num order by psrh.generation_date) as first_occr,
				CASE
					WHEN gqcl.case_id IS NULL THEN
						DENSE_RANK() over (PARTITION BY
							TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
							' - ' ||
							TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD')
							ORDER BY
								psrh.generation_date)
					ELSE 0
				END
			AS empty_period
			,PFH.rec_num as p_rec_num
			,cai.ae_rec_num
			,cai.mdr_ae_soc
			,cai.mdr_ae_soc_code
			,cai.mdr_ae_pt_code
			,cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id
			,psrh.submission_date
			,conser_listedness
			,CASE
				WHEN cai.mdr_ae_soc IS NOT NULL
				THEN cai.mdr_ae_pt
				END AS pt
			, CASE 
				WHEN pate2b.case_id IS NOT NULL THEN NVL(gen.gender,'不明')
			ELSE 
				CASE 
					WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id IS NOT NULL  THEN
					CASE 
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_desc IS NULL THEN cpc.patient_sex_desc
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id NOT IN (1,2,3) THEN '不明'
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id in (1,2,3) THEN (SELECT gender from vw_lg_gender where gender_id=cpc.patient_sex_id and lang_id=25)  
					END						
					ELSE NVL(cpc.patient_sex_desc,'不明')
				END
			END  AS gender
			, CASE WHEN pate2b.case_id is not null THEN pate2b.PATIENT_AGE_ONSET_NUM
			ELSE CASE
				WHEN
					CPC.PATIENT_AGE_GROUP_ID = 1 			--ci.flag_child_case = 1
				THEN
					case when upper(parg.e2b_code) <> 810 AND (NVL2(parg.age_unit,cparc.gestation_period_num,NULL) is not null) then
				 '妊娠'  end || NVL2(parg.age_unit,cparc.gestation_period_num,NULL)
				||
				NVL2(cparc.gestation_period_num,parg.age_unit,NULL)
				WHEN NVL(CPC.PATIENT_AGE_GROUP_ID,0) <> 1		--nvl(ci.flag_child_case,0) = 0 
				THEN
					CASE
						WHEN cpc.patient_age_onset_num IS NULL THEN pudgr.e2b_DESC
						WHEN nvl(pudp.e2b_code,000) <> 800 
						then  NVL2(pudp.age_unit,cpc.patient_age_onset_num,NULL) 
						||
						NVL2(cpc.patient_age_onset_num,pudp.age_unit,NULL)
						WHEN cpc.patient_age_onset_num = 1 then '10歳未満'
						ELSE (cpc.patient_age_onset_num - 1) || '0' || '歳代'
					END
			END
			END
			AS age
			,TO_CHAR(cai.date_ae_start) AS onset_date
			,case when ci.case_num is not null
				then case when cai.outcome IN (1,2,3,4,5) then '[' || cai.outcome || ']' else '[0]' end
			 end AS outcome
			,Case when ci.case_num is not null then CASE
				WHEN cai.infection = 1
					THEN '感染症'
				ELSE '副作用' END 
            END AS Event_Classification	,
			vlr.report_type 
                         || chr(10) ||
			ci.case_num AS Survey_name,
			ci.case_id,
			ci.tenant_id,
			ci.version_num,
			--vrpa.pmda_number
			CASE
				WHEN cai.mdr_ae_soc IS NOT NULL
					THEN CASE
							WHEN conser_listedness = 1
								THEN NULL
							ELSE vrpa.pmda_number
							END
				END pmda_number
		FROM (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id,
MAX(processed_report_id) processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num,
						min(agg_report_id) agg_report_id
				from gtt_query_case_list
                group by case_id,tenant_id,ae_rec_num) gqcl
		LEFT JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa ON (
				NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
			AND
				NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
			AND
				NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
		)
		LEFT JOIN l_identification ci ON (
				gqcl.case_id = ci.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = ci.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = ci.version_num
				)
                INNER JOIN (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id, 
						processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num
				from v_j_ae_iden_reaction
                group by case_id,tenant_id,processed_report_id,ae_rec_num
               union all
                select  1,1,1,-1,1 from dual) cai_max

                (
                  cai_max.case_id = nvl(gqcl.case_id,1)

                  cai_max.tenant_id = nvl(gqcl.tenant_id,1)
                  AND 
                  cai_max.processed_report_id = nvl(gqcl.processed_report_id,-1)
                  AND
                  cai_max.ae_rec_num = nvl(gqcl.ae_rec_num,1)
                )
		INNER JOIN 
           (select
            CASE_ID,
            TENANT_ID,
            VERSION_NUM,
            AE_REC_NUM,
            PROCESSED_REPORT_ID,
            DATE_AE_START,
            MDR_AE_SOC,
            MDR_AE_SOC_CODE,
            AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID,
            MDR_AE_PT_CODE,
            MDR_AE_PT,
            OUTCOME,
            INFECTION 
		from
            v_j_ae_iden_reaction 
        union all
        SELECT
            1 as CASE_ID,
            1 as TENANT_ID,
            1 as VERSION_NUM,
            1 as AE_REC_NUM,
            -1 as PROCESSED_REPORT_ID,
            NULL as DATE_AE_START,
            NULL as MDR_AE_SOC,
            NULL as MDR_AE_SOC_CODE,
            NULL as AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID,
            NULL as MDR_AE_PT_CODE,
            NULL as MDR_AE_PT,
            NULL as OUTCOME,
            NULL as INFECTION
        FROM 
		    DUAL
		)
                cai ON (
				cai_max.case_id = cai.case_id
				AND cai_max.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
				AND cai_max.version_num = cai.version_num
				AND cai_max.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num
                                AND cai_max.processed_report_id = cai.processed_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN V_SUB_PATIENT_CHARACTERISTICS pate2b ON (
				gqcl.case_id = pate2b.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = pate2b.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = pate2b.version_num
AND gqcl.processed_report_id=pate2b.processed_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN l_patient_characteristics cpc ON (
				gqcl.case_id = cpc.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = cpc.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = cpc.version_num
				)
		LEFT JOIN l_parent_characteristics cparc ON (
				gqcl.case_id = cparc.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = cparc.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = cparc.version_num
				)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
				)
                LEFT JOIN period_det pd ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = pd.agg_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN conservative_listedness gtt ON ( cai.mdr_ae_pt_code=gtt.mdr_ae_pt_code
			/*	gqcl.case_id = gtt.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = gtt.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = gtt.version_num
				AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = gtt.ae_rec_num*/
				)
        left join vw_lg_gender gen on (pate2b.patient_sex_id=gen.e2b_code
 	    AND gen.lang_id=25
            AND gen.PARENT_FLAG=1)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lrty_report_type vlr ON (
			ci.source_type_id = vlr.rpt_type_id
			and ci.tenant_id = vlr.tenant_id
			and vlr.lang_id = 25
		)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lau_age_unit pudp ON
		(cpc.patient_age_onset_unit_id = pudp.age_unit_id 
		and pudp.lang_id = 25)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lau_age_unit parg ON
            (UPPER(cparc.gestation_period_unit_id)  = UPPER(parg.age_unit_id)
            and parg.lang_id=25
                )
          LEFT JOIN vw_lau_age_unit panp ON
            (UPPER(cpc.GESTATION_PERIOD_UNIT_ID)  = UPPER(panp.age_unit_id)
              and panp.lang_id=25)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_e2b_desc pudg ON
		(UPPER(panp.AGE_UNIT)  = UPPER(pudg.lm_desc) and pudg.key_id = 'GESTATION_PERIOD_UNIT_R3_J'
			)
	    LEFT JOIN vw_lag_age_group vlag ON
              (cpc.patient_age_group_id = vlag.age_group_id
              and vlag.lang_id=25)

		LEFT JOIN pvr_e2b_desc pudgr ON
		( UPPER(vlag.age_group)  = UPPER(pudgr.lm_desc) and pudgr.key_id = 'AGE_GROUP_R3_J'
			)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_psr_form_4_submitted_data pfh on (cai.case_id = pfh.case_id and nvl(pfh.deleted_flag,0) = 0 and pfh.rec_num <> -999 and pfh.agg_report_id
		in (select distinct agg_report_id from gtt_query_case_list where agg_report_id not in 
        (select to_number(param_value) from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='OBJECT_ID')))
	) 
	,set_2 as (
	Select case_id,min(rn) n_rec_num from set_1  where p_rec_num is null group by case_id
		) 
	,set_3 as (
	Select case_id,row_number() over (order by n_rec_num) n_rec_num from set_2 where case_id is not null
		) 
        , final_data as(
	SELECT
	'第'|| period_num  || '回' "PERIOD_NUM",
	case when p_rec_num is not null then p_rec_num 
    else ( (Select nvl(max(rec_num),0) from pvr_psr_form_4_submitted_data where NVL(deleted_flag,0) <> 1 and agg_report_id in (select distinct agg_report_id from gtt_query_case_list where agg_report_id not in 
        (select to_number(param_value) from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='OBJECT_ID'))
)
            + n_rec_num 
        ) end  as "REC_NUM",
	mdr_ae_soc "MDR_AE_SOC",
	mdr_Ae_soc_code "MDR_AE_SOC_CODE",
	pt "MDR_AE_PT",
	mdr_ae_pt_code "MDR_AE_PT_CODE",
	ae_rec_num "AE_REC_NUM",
	gender "GENDER",
	age "AGE",
	onset_date "ONSET_DATE", 
	outcome "OUTCOME",
	Event_Classification "EVENT_CLASSIFICATION",
	set_1.Survey_name "SURVEY_NAME",
	pmda_number  "PMDA_ACK_NUM",
	set_1.case_id "CASE_ID", 
(	SELECT DISTINCT
			'''MedDRA/J Version(' ||
			version_number ||
			')''' AS mdr_ver
		FROM
			vw_meddra_tenant_mapping 
        WHERE tenant_id = PKG_PVR_APP_UTIL.F_GET_ACTIVE_TENANT(1) 
) "MEDDRA_VER",
    ae_soc_intl_rank_id "AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID",
	submission_date "SUBMISSION_DATE",
    set_1.tenant_id,set_1.version_num
	FROM set_1 left join set_3 on (set_1.case_id = set_3.case_id)
	where (set_1.first_occr = 1 or set_1.empty_period = 1)) 
    select 	cm.PERIOD_NUM     "PERIOD_NUM",
			cm.REC_NUM      "REC_NUM",
			cm.MDR_AE_SOC             "MDR_AE_SOC",
			cm.MDR_AE_SOC_CODE     "MDR_AE_SOC_CODE",
			cm.MDR_AE_PT     "MDR_AE_PT",
			cm.MDR_AE_PT_CODE      "MDR_AE_PT_CODE",
			cm.AE_REC_NUM      "AE_REC_NUM",
			cm.GENDER       "GENDER",
			cm.AGE        "AGE",
			cm.ONSET_DATE      "ONSET_DATE",
			cm.OUTCOME       "OUTCOME",
			cm.EVENT_CLASSIFICATION   "EVENT_CLASSIFICATION",
			cm.SURVEY_NAME       "SURVEY_NAME"     ,
			cm.PMDA_ACK_NUM   "PMDA_ACK_NUM"        ,
			cm.case_id       "CASE_ID" ,
			cm.meddra_ver       "MEDDRA_VER" ,
			cm.ae_soc_intl_rank_id    "AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID",
			cm.submission_date "SUBMISSION_DATE"
 FROM final_data  cm

customSQLTemplateSelectFrom:
WITH v_prod AS (          
         SELECT
            LISTAGG(
                CASE
                    WHEN vpj.product_name IS NOT NULL THEN vpj.product_name ||
                    case when vlf.formulation is not null or (vpj.concentration_text is not null and vluj.unit is not null ) then '(' ||
                        case when vlf.formulation is not null then vlf.formulation end ||
                        case when (vpj.concentration_text is not null and vluj.unit is not null ) then ', ' end ||
                        vpj.concentration_text ||
                        vluj.unit ||
                        ')'
                    END
                END,
            CHR(10) ) WITHIN GROUP(ORDER BY vpj.product_name) AS DELIVERY_QUANTITY
        FROM
            (SELECT
                gtt.code
            FROM
                gtt_filter_key_values gtt
            WHERE
                gtt.key_id = (select KEY_ID from pvr_filter_dict where group_desc='PRODUCT')) gvp
            JOIN vw_product_j vpj ON (
                gvp.code = vpj.product_id
            )
            LEFT JOIN vw_lfor_formulation_j vlf ON (
                vpj.formulation_id = vlf.formulation_id
            )
            LEFT JOIN vw_ldu_unit_j vluj ON (
                vpj.concentration_unit_id = vluj.unit_id
            )
            ) , v_reg_pmda_auth AS (
                SELECT  distinct
                    case_id,
                    tenant_id,
                    version_num
                FROM
                     reg_pmda_auth_identification
                WHERE REPORT_TYPE_ID in (1,2)
                UNION
                SELECT 1, 1, 1 FROM dual
            ),
        conservative_listedness AS (
                select mdr_ae_pt_code, pkg_pvr_app_util.f_conservative_listedness(null,NULL,mdr_ae_pt_code) conser_listedness 
            from (select distinct mdr_ae_pt_code from v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai
            where exists (select 1 from gtt_query_case_list gqcl where gqcl.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND gqcl.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND gqcl.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num)
              and mdr_ae_pt_code is not null
                    )), 
        set_1 AS (
            SELECT
                cai.case_id,
                cai.mdr_ae_soc,
                cai.mdr_ae_soc_code,
                cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                cai.mdr_ae_pt_code,
                    CASE
                        WHEN cai.mdr_ae_pt IS NOT NULL THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN conser_listedness = 1  THEN 
                                cai.mdr_ae_pt
                                ELSE '*' ||
                                cai.mdr_ae_pt
                            END
                    END
                AS mdr_ae_pt,
                cai.ae_rec_num,
                cai.infection,
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS REPT_PERIOD,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY
                    cai.case_id,
                    cai.ae_rec_num
                    ORDER BY
                        cai.ae_rec_num desc, psrh.generation_date
                ) rn_1,
                DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY
                    cai.case_id,
                    cai.ae_rec_num
                    ORDER BY
                        psrh.generation_date
                ) rn,
                    CASE
                        WHEN gqcl.case_id IS NULL THEN
                            DENSE_RANK() over (PARTITION BY
                                TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                                ' - ' ||
                                TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD')
                                ORDER BY
                                    psrh.generation_date)
                        ELSE 0
                    END
                AS rn2
            FROM 
( select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id,
						MAX(processed_report_id) over (partition by case_id,tenant_id,ae_rec_num) processed_report_id,
						version_num version_num,
						agg_report_id agg_report_id
				from gtt_query_case_list ) GQCL
                JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa on (
                NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
                )
               INNER JOIN (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id, 
						MAX(processed_report_id) processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num
				from v_j_ae_iden_reaction
                group by case_id,tenant_id,processed_report_id,ae_rec_num) cai_max
                ON
                (
                  cai_max.case_id = gqcl.case_id
                  AND
                  cai_max.tenant_id = gqcl.tenant_id
                  AND 
                  cai_max.processed_report_id = gqcl.processed_report_id
                  AND
                  cai_max.ae_rec_num = gqcl.ae_rec_num
                )
                INNER JOIN v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai ON (
                        cai_max.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND
                        cai_max.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND
                        cai_max.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND
                        cai_max.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num
                    AND 
                        cai_max.processed_report_id = cai.processed_report_id
                )
                LEFT JOIN conservative_listedness gtt ON ( cai.mdr_ae_pt_code=gtt.mdr_ae_pt_code
      /*                  gqcl.case_id = gtt.case_id
                    AND
                        gqcl.tenant_id = gtt.tenant_id
                    AND
                        gqcl.version_num = gtt.version_num
                    AND
                        gqcl.ae_rec_num = gtt.ae_rec_num*/
                )
                LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
                    gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
                )
        )
       , set_period AS (
            SELECT
                
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS REPT_PERIOD,
                psrh.generation_date,
                row_number() over(partition by TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_START_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(PSRH.REPORT_END_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') order by psrh.generation_date desc ) period_number
            FROM GTT_QUERY_CASE_LIST GQCL
                JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa on (
                NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
            AND
                NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
                )
                LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
                    gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
                )
        ) 
        ,set_2 AS (
            SELECT
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                case_id,
                rept_period
            FROM
                set_1
            WHERE
                (rn_1 = 1 OR rn2 = 1)
        ),set_3 AS (
            SELECT
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                nvl(set_2.rept_period,set_period.rept_period) rept_period,
                DECODE(COUNT(DISTINCT case_id),0,NULL,COUNT(DISTINCT case_id)) AS case_count
            FROM
                set_2
            right join set_period on (set_2.rept_period=set_period.rept_period and set_period.period_number=1)
            GROUP BY
                mdr_ae_soc,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                nvl(set_2.rept_period,set_period.rept_period)
                --rept_period
        ),evt_2 AS (
            SELECT
                case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                DECODE(infection,1,1,0) AS flag_infection,
                rept_period
            FROM
                set_1
            WHERE
                rn_1 = 1
        ),evt_3 AS (
          SELECT case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                rept_period,
                COUNT(DISTINCT CASE_ID||'-'||MDR_AE_SOC||'-'||MDR_AE_PT_CODE) EVT_COUNT,
                SUM(flag_infection) AS inf_count
            FROM (   SELECT
                            case_id,
                            mdr_ae_soc,
                            mdr_ae_pt_code,
                            mdr_ae_pt,
                            rept_period,
                            CASE WHEN ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY CASE_ID,MDR_AE_SOC,MDR_AE_PT_CODE,flag_infection ORDER BY NULL) =1 THEN flag_infection ELSE 0 END flag_infection
                        FROM evt_2 )
            GROUP BY case_id,
                mdr_ae_soc,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                mdr_ae_pt,
                rept_period            
        ) 
        , PSR_FORM_3 AS (SELECT
                set_3.mdr_ae_soc,
                evt_3.mdr_ae_pt,
                DECODE(SET_3.REPT_PERIOD,' - ',
                TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_START_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
                ' - ' ||
                TO_CHAR(TO_DATE((select param_value from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='REPORT_END_DATE'),'dd-mm-yyyy'),'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                SET_3.REPT_PERIOD
                ) AS REPT_PERIOD,
                set_3.case_count soc_count,
                evt_3.evt_count ||
                CASE
                        WHEN inf_count <> 0   THEN '(' ||
                        inf_count ||
                        ')'
                    END
                AS pt_count,
(	SELECT DISTINCT
			'''MedDRA/J Version(' ||
			version_number ||
			')''' AS mdr_ver
		FROM
			vw_meddra_tenant_mapping 
        WHERE tenant_id = PKG_PVR_APP_UTIL.F_GET_ACTIVE_TENANT(1) 
)  meddra_ver,
                (SELECT DELIVERY_QUANTITY FROM V_PROD) delivery_qty,
                ae_soc_intl_rank_id,
                mdr_ae_pt_code,
                evt_3.case_id
            FROM
                set_3
                LEFT JOIN evt_3 ON (
                        NVL(set_3.mdr_ae_soc,000001) = NVL(evt_3.mdr_ae_soc,000001)
                    AND
                        set_3.rept_period = evt_3.rept_period
                )) 
                , CUMM_SOC_COUNT AS (SELECT         mdr_ae_soc, ae_soc_intl_rank_id, DECODE(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE_ID),0,NULL,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE_ID)) cumm_count
                FROM        psr_form_3
                GROUP BY    mdr_ae_soc, ae_soc_intl_rank_id) 
                SELECT distinct A.mdr_ae_soc "MDR_AE_SOC",
        A.mdr_Ae_pt "MDR_AE_PT",
        A.rept_period "REPT_PERIOD",
        A.soc_count "SOC_COUNT",
        A.pt_count "PT_COUNT",
        A.meddra_ver "MEDDRA_VER",
        A.delivery_qty "DELIVERY_QTY",
        A.ae_soc_intl_rank_id "AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID",
        A.mdr_ae_pt_code "MDR_AE_PT_CODE",

WITH v_reg_pmda_auth AS (
SELECT
case_id,
tenant_id,
version_num,
LISTAGG(identification_number,',') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY identification_number) as pmda_number
FROM
(Select distinct a.case_id,a.tenant_id,a.version_num,
max(a.REPORT_TYPE_DESC||'-'||a.IDENTIFICATION_NUMBER ) identification_number 
from REG_PMDA_AUTH_IDENTIFICATION a
join gtt_filter_key_values b on (a.auth_id = b.code and b.key_id = 17 and a.identification_number is not null) join vw_trade_name_dsp c on (c.license_type_id = 4 and c.license_id = a.auth_id)
 where REGEXP_LIKE(a.REPORT_TYPE_DESC, '^[[:alpha:]]+$') group by a.case_id,a.tenant_id,a.version_num) rpai
GROUP BY
case_id,tenant_id,version_num
union
select 1,1,1,null from dual
), conservative_listedness AS (
				select mdr_ae_pt_code, pkg_pvr_app_util.f_conservative_listedness(null,NULL,mdr_ae_pt_code) conser_listedness 
            from (select distinct mdr_ae_pt_code from v_j_ae_iden_reaction cai
            where exists (select 1 from gtt_query_case_list gqcl where gqcl.case_id = cai.case_id
                    AND gqcl.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
                    AND gqcl.version_num = cai.version_num
                    AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num)
          and mdr_ae_pt_code is not null
                    )),
period_det as
(
select gqcl.agg_Report_id,gqcl.tenant_id, dense_rank() over (order by psrh.agg_report_id,psrh.generation_date) as period_num 
from
(select distinct agg_Report_id,tenant_id from gtt_query_case_list) gqcl
LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
				and gqcl.tenant_id = psrh.tenant_id
				))
,set_1 AS (
			SELECT DISTINCT TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') || ' - ' || TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') AS rept_period
			,pd.period_num as period_num
			,case when pfh.rec_num is null then row_number() OVER ( partition by psrh.agg_report_id,psrh.generation_date
				ORDER BY cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id,cai.mdr_ae_pt_code,psrh.submission_date,cai.case_id
				) else pfh.rec_num end as rn,
			dense_rank() over (partition by gqcl.case_id,cai.mdr_ae_soc,cai.mdr_Ae_pt,cai.ae_rec_num order by psrh.generation_date desc) as first_occr,
				CASE
					WHEN gqcl.case_id IS NULL THEN
						DENSE_RANK() over (PARTITION BY
							TO_CHAR(psrh.report_start_date,'YYYY-MM-DD') ||
							' - ' ||
							TO_CHAR(psrh.report_end_date,'YYYY-MM-DD')
							ORDER BY
								psrh.generation_date)
					ELSE 0
				END
			AS empty_period
			,PFH.rec_num as p_rec_num
			,cai.ae_rec_num
			,cai.mdr_ae_soc
			,cai.mdr_ae_soc_code
			,cai.mdr_ae_pt_code
			,cai.ae_soc_intl_rank_id
			,psrh.submission_date
			,conser_listedness
			,CASE
				WHEN cai.mdr_ae_soc IS NOT NULL
					THEN CASE
							WHEN conser_listedness = 1
								THEN 
                                                                 cai.mdr_ae_pt
							ELSE '*' || cai.mdr_ae_pt
							END
				END AS pt
			, CASE 
				WHEN pate2b.case_id IS NOT NULL THEN NVL(gen.gender,'不明')
			ELSE 
				CASE 
					WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id IS NOT NULL  THEN
					CASE 
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_desc IS NULL THEN cpc.patient_sex_desc
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id NOT IN (1,2,3) THEN '不明'
						WHEN cpc.patient_sex_id in (1,2,3) THEN cpc.patient_sex_desc 
					END						
					ELSE NVL(cpc.patient_sex_desc,'不明')
				END
			END  AS gender
			, CASE WHEN pate2b.case_id is not null THEN pate2b.PATIENT_AGE_ONSET_NUM
			ELSE CASE
				WHEN
					CPC.PATIENT_AGE_GROUP_ID = 7  			--ci.flag_child_case = 1
				THEN
					case when upper(parg.e2b_code) <> 810 AND (NVL2(parg.age_unit,cparc.gestation_period_num,NULL) is not null) then
				 '妊娠'  end || NVL2(parg.age_unit,cparc.gestation_period_num,NULL)
				||
				NVL2(cparc.gestation_period_num,parg.age_unit,NULL)
				WHEN NVL(CPC.PATIENT_AGE_GROUP_ID,0) <> 7		--nvl(ci.flag_child_case,0) = 0 
				THEN
					CASE
						WHEN cpc.patient_age_onset_num IS NULL THEN pudgr.e2b_DESC
						WHEN nvl(pudp.e2b_code,000) <> 800 
						then  NVL2(pudp.age_unit,cpc.patient_age_onset_num,NULL) 
						||
						NVL2(cpc.patient_age_onset_num,pudp.age_unit,NULL)
						WHEN cpc.patient_age_onset_num = 1 then '10歳未満'
						ELSE (cpc.patient_age_onset_num - 1) || '0' || '歳代'
					END
			END
			END
			AS age
			,TO_CHAR(cai.date_ae_start) AS onset_date
			,case when ci.case_num is not null
				then case when cai.outcome IN (1,2,3,4,5) then '[' || cai.outcome || ']' else '[0]' end
			 end AS outcome
			,Case when ci.case_num is not null then CASE
				WHEN cai.infection = 1
					THEN '感染症'
				ELSE '副作用' END 
            END AS Event_Classification	,
			vlr.report_type 
                         || chr(10) ||
			ci.case_num AS Survey_name,
			ci.case_id,
			ci.tenant_id,
			ci.version_num,
			--vrpa.pmda_number
			CASE
				WHEN cai.mdr_ae_soc IS NOT NULL
					THEN CASE
							WHEN conser_listedness = 1
								THEN NULL
							ELSE vrpa.pmda_number
							END
				END pmda_number
		FROM (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id,
MAX(processed_report_id) processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num,
						min(agg_report_id) agg_report_id
				from gtt_query_case_list
                group by case_id,tenant_id,ae_rec_num) gqcl
		LEFT JOIN v_reg_pmda_auth vrpa ON (
				NVL(gqcl.case_id,1) = vrpa.case_id
			AND
				NVL(gqcl.tenant_id,1) = vrpa.tenant_id
			AND
				NVL(gqcl.version_num,1) = vrpa.version_num
		)
		LEFT JOIN l_identification ci ON (
				gqcl.case_id = ci.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = ci.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = ci.version_num
				)
                INNER JOIN (	select 	ae_rec_num,
						case_id,
						tenant_id, 
						processed_report_id,
						max(version_num) version_num
				from v_j_ae_iden_reaction
                group by case_id,tenant_id,processed_report_id,ae_rec_num
               union all
                select  1,1,1,-1,1 from dual) cai_max
                ON
                (
                  cai_max.case_id = nvl(gqcl.case_id,1)
                  AND
                  cai_max.tenant_id = nvl(gqcl.tenant_id,1)
                  AND 
                  cai_max.processed_report_id = nvl(gqcl.processed_report_id,-1)
                  AND
                  cai_max.ae_rec_num = nvl(gqcl.ae_rec_num,1)
                )
		INNER JOIN 
           (select
            CASE_ID,
            TENANT_ID,
            VERSION_NUM,
            AE_REC_NUM,
            PROCESSED_REPORT_ID,
            DATE_AE_START,
            MDR_AE_SOC,
            MDR_AE_SOC_CODE,
            AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID,
            MDR_AE_PT_CODE,
            MDR_AE_PT,
            OUTCOME,
            INFECTION 
		from
            v_j_ae_iden_reaction 
        union all
        SELECT
            1 as CASE_ID,
            1 as TENANT_ID,
            1 as VERSION_NUM,
            1 as AE_REC_NUM,
            -1 as PROCESSED_REPORT_ID,
            NULL as DATE_AE_START,
            NULL as MDR_AE_SOC,
            NULL as MDR_AE_SOC_CODE,
            NULL as AE_SOC_INTL_RANK_ID,
            NULL as MDR_AE_PT_CODE,
            NULL as MDR_AE_PT,
            NULL as OUTCOME,
            NULL as INFECTION
        FROM 
		    DUAL
		)
                cai ON (
				cai_max.case_id = cai.case_id
				AND cai_max.tenant_id = cai.tenant_id
				AND cai_max.version_num = cai.version_num
				AND cai_max.ae_rec_num = cai.ae_rec_num
                                AND cai_max.processed_report_id = cai.processed_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN V_SUB_PATIENT_CHARACTERISTICS pate2b ON (
				gqcl.case_id = pate2b.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = pate2b.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = pate2b.version_num
AND gqcl.processed_report_id=pate2b.processed_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN l_patient_characteristics cpc ON (
				gqcl.case_id = cpc.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = cpc.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = cpc.version_num
				)
		LEFT JOIN l_parent_characteristics cparc ON (
				gqcl.case_id = cparc.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = cparc.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = cparc.version_num
				)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_submission_report_history psrh ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = psrh.agg_report_id
				)
                LEFT JOIN period_det pd ON (
				gqcl.agg_report_id = pd.agg_report_id
				)
		LEFT JOIN conservative_listedness gtt ON ( cai.mdr_ae_pt_code=gtt.mdr_ae_pt_code
			/*	gqcl.case_id = gtt.case_id
				AND gqcl.tenant_id = gtt.tenant_id
				AND gqcl.version_num = gtt.version_num
				AND gqcl.ae_rec_num = gtt.ae_rec_num*/
				)
 left join vw_lg_gender_j gen on (pate2b.patient_sex_id=gen.e2b_code)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lrty_report_type_j vlr ON (
			ci.source_type_id = vlr.rpt_type_id
			and ci.tenant_id = vlr.tenant_id
		)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lau_age_unit_j pudp ON
		(cpc.patient_age_onset_unit_id = pudp.age_unit_id 
			)
		LEFT JOIN vw_lau_age_unit_j parg ON
            (UPPER(cparc.gestation_period_unit_id)  = UPPER(parg.age_unit_id)
                )
		LEFT JOIN pvr_e2b_desc pudg ON
		(UPPER(cpc.gestation_period_unit_desc)  = UPPER(pudg.lm_desc) and pudg.key_id = 'GESTATION_PERIOD_UNIT_R3_J'
			)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_e2b_desc pudgr ON
		(UPPER(cpc.patient_age_group_desc)     = UPPER(pudgr.lm_desc) and pudgr.key_id = 'AGE_GROUP_R3_J'
			)
		LEFT JOIN pvr_psr_form_4_submitted_data pfh on (cai.case_id = pfh.case_id and nvl(pfh.deleted_flag,0) = 0 and pfh.rec_num <> -999 and pfh.agg_report_id
		in (select distinct agg_report_id from gtt_query_case_list where agg_report_id not in 
        (select to_number(param_value) from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='OBJECT_ID')))
	) 
	,set_2 as (
	Select case_id,min(rn) n_rec_num from set_1  where p_rec_num is null group by case_id
		) 
	,set_3 as (
	Select case_id,row_number() over (order by n_rec_num) n_rec_num from set_2 where case_id is not null
		)

        , final_data as(

    else ( (Select nvl(max(rec_num),0) from pvr_psr_form_4_submitted_data where NVL(deleted_flag,0) <> 1 and agg_report_id in (select distinct agg_report_id from gtt_query_case_list where agg_report_id not in 
        (select to_number(param_value) from gtt_report_input_params where param_key='OBJECT_ID'))
)
            + n_rec_num 
        ) end  as "REC_NUM",
	mdr_ae_soc "MDR_AE_SOC",
